</nav><div class="Web__section"><h1>Trial by Trolley™ on PlayingCards.io</h1><img class="LandingPage__image" src="../img/landing/trial-by-trolley.png"><div class="StartGameButton"><div class="StartGameButton__button"><div class="Throbber Throbber--small Throbber--dark"></div><button class="StartGameButton__create-single" data-template="tbt">Start Game</button><button class="StartGameButton__create-bulk" data-template="tbt"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 64 512"><path d="M32 224c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32s-14.3 32-32 32-32-14.3-32-32 14.3-32 32-32zM0 136c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32-14.3-32-32-32-32 14.3-32 32zm0 240c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32-14.3-32-32-32-32 14.3-32 32z"/></svg></button></div></div><div class="LandingPage__instructions"><p>Trial by Trolley™ is a real card game and better played with friends! This is a Trial by Trolley demo, enjoy these 120 cards and play all 500 cards when you buy the game on <a href="../../https@amzn.to/2Maf5h8">Amazon</a>, <a href="../../https@bit.ly/2MafgZQ">Target</a> or <a href="../../https@bit.ly/2M4rsLs">Walmart.com</a>. PlayingCards.io is a virtual tabletop to help you experience the game for a limited time during quarantine, all rights to Trial By Trolley 2020.</p>
<h2 id="trial-by-trolley™-rules">Trial by Trolley™ Rules</h2>
<p>For 3-8 players.</p>
<p>Each round is started by designating one player as the conductor and splitting the remaining players into two teams. Each team is assigned to one side of the track.</p>
<img src="../img/trial-by-trolley/tutorial-1.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;">

<p>One player on each team draws 3 innocent cards, one player on each team draws 3 guilty cards, and one player on each team draws 3 modifier cards.</p>
<img src="../img/trial-by-trolley/tutorial-2.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;">

<h2 id="building-the-board">Building the Board</h2>
<p>Each team draws a random innocent card and places it in the first slot on their side of the track.</p>
<img src="../img/trial-by-trolley/tutorial-3.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;">

<p>The two players that drew innocent cards each place a card in the second slot on their side of the track.</p>
<img src="../img/trial-by-trolley/tutorial-4.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;">

<p>The two players that drew guilty cards each place a card in the third slot on the opponents track.</p>
<img src="../img/trial-by-trolley/tutorial-5.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;">

<p>And the two players that drew modifier cards each place a card in the modifier slots anywhere on the board, on either side.</p>
<img src="../img/trial-by-trolley/tutorial-6.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;">

<h2 id="debate">Debate</h2>
<p>Now that the board is completed, all players debate to convince the conductor to choose which side dies. When each side has made their case, the conductor decides and all of the characters on the losing side are murdered by a trolley. Each player on the losing side receives a death token. All cards are discarded and the next conductor is chosen.</p>
<img src="../img/trial-by-trolley/tutorial-7.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;">

<p>Have fun!</p>
